4 hundred forty dollars ($340) per month in the case of two (2) children, four
5 hundred dollars ($400) per month in the case of three (3) children, and four
6 hundred forty dollars ($440) per month in the case of four (4) or more
7 children. Benefits under this subsection shall apply in addition to benefits
8 which may be payable under subsections (1) and (3) of this section.
